snippet.title: Obscure GBC Gaming 4 - Hello Kitty no Sweet Adventure: Daniel-kun ni Aitai
snippet.description: Hello Kitty no Sweet Adventure: Daniel-kun ni Aitai is platform video game. Its based on famous character series from Sanrio. Just like Pokemon games, this game exist in two versions. Different by using different main character. Other version is Dear Daniel no Sweet Adventure: Kitty-chan wo Sagashite. It also have sequel Hello Kitty to Dear Daniel no Dream Adventure.
